      <title>油价突破窄幅区间后涨势因中国问题而停滞</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-3</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对中国经济衰退的担忧导致整体市场出现波动，油价从近三个月来的最高水平回落。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/latest-oil-market-news-and-analysis-for-jan-3</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 23:32:19 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场综述：中国问题影响市场人气，股市涨跌互现</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于对中国经济放缓的担忧蔓延至市场，且投资者期待新的美国经济数据，在假期缩短且动荡的一周结束时，股市涨跌互现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-01-02/stock-market-today-dow-s-p-live-updates</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 02 Jan 2025 22:26:22 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>南非兰特八年来首次成为领先的新兴市场货币</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/how-south-africa-s-rand-zar-usd-became-a-top-five-currency-performer-in-em</link>
      <description><![CDATA[法国农业信贷银行 (Credit Agricole SA) 和阿什莫尔集团 (Ashmore Group Plc) 的分析师表示，自 2016 年以来，南非兰特首次跻身年度表现最佳的五种新兴市场货币之列，而且未来可能还会有更多表现。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-12-31/how-south-africa-s-rand-zar-usd-became-a-top-five-currency-performer-in-em</guid>
